---
title: Sticky Sweet Chilli Pork Bao Buns with Potato Fries & Oyster Sauce Greens
description: It’s that time again - get ready to bao down to flavour town! Tender pork loin is tossed in a rich sweet chilli sauce before being
added to fluffy, steamy bao buns. Served alongside much-loved potato fries and flavourful greens, this dish ticks all the boxes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65bc53fe23af27a6dfb312b1-5dd0787f.jpeg
